t: Pacific Gold - Wikipedia
s: April 13, 2025 - Pacific Gold is an American Christian music band from Seattle, Washington. Their members include Torry Anderson, Brian Hibbard, Dan Koch, John Raines, and David Stuart. The band independently released its debut EPs, The River and The Holly & the Ivy, in 2012.
